description: For sale: $460,000. ONLY 4 UNITS REMAIN. Estimated completion of Lakeside at Lyndale Gardens is July 2020. 2 bedroom 2 bathroom homes are 1418 finished square feet starting at $460000. Each 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home will be generously sized at about 1418 finished square feet. The Lakeside project is designed to take advantage of the views of Richfield Lake and all homes will have a lake view. Homes are also designed to bring abundant natural light to the interior with floor to ceiling windows on both the front and rear of the home. End unit homes will feature clerestory windows in the master bedroom to allow extra light. First floor homes will feature a private deck facing the lake and a private patio off the master bedroom. The private patio will walk out to the green space on the main entrance side of the building which is perfect for a pet owner or an owner wanting a walk out feature in their new home. All Lakeside homes will feature high ceilings, generous room sizes, clean lines and quality finishes.

Zestimate® Home Value: $283,305. This home is a Real Estate Owned (REO)/Post Foreclosure. Once a lender has foreclosed on a property it is soon put up for public auction. If bids fall short of the asking price the bank will buy back the home and attempt to sell it on the open market. However, lenders are not real estate agents, meaning that they will often accept offers 30 to 60 percent less than market value!

description: Recently sold: $431,000.

Recently sold: $250,000. This lovely, spacious 1946 rambler is LOADED with charm and character!  There are two bedrooms on the main floor, and two non-conforming bedrooms on the fully finished lower level.  You'll also find a family room/den on both the main and lower levels. TWO fireplaces (one gas-burning, the other wood-burning) make for extra cozy spaces in the chilly months while the large deck and spacious, fenced back yard are perfect for hosting late-summer barbecues!  Don't miss this beauty in the heart of Richfield.

Contact listing agent Ryan Luthi for more information: ryan@fultonrealty.com 612-406-6020

Recently sold: $255,000. A charming single family home located on a elevated corner lot with refinished hardwood floors throughout the main floor. Two fully renovated bathrooms with new tub/shower faucets and vanities. A spacious, fully fenced backyard centered around a secluded built-in grill and outdoor fireplace which is flanked by a cedar pergola perfect for hosting friends and family. Two car garage.
Recently sold: $310,000.

description: Recently sold: $275,000. Updated & very desirable 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath brick rambler on a corner lot with many special features! Updated kitchen with newer stove, refrigerator & disposal. 2 fireplaces with brick surround, large living room with a beautiful picture window. Hardwood floors underneath carpet on main level. Lovely coved ceilings. Lower level features a 4th (non-conforming) bedroom, office and family room with a brick fireplace. Central vacuum, in-ground sprinkler system, leaf guard gutters and spouts. Newer hot water heater and replacement windows. Lots of extra storage and shelving in basement with a workbench. Privacy fence in nice size backyard with many pretty perennials. Close to High School, Community Center & Parks. Your buyers will love this home!.

description:
Recently sold: $133,000. Ground level studio-style apartment, with a very open layout, in a fabulous location (494 & Lyndale--quick access to 35W) with several onsite amenities: underground heated/cooled garage, storage unit, exercise room, party room, and shops and restaurants just steps away!



Neighborhood Description



LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! Complex is just off Lyndale and 494 (also a major bus line), with quick and easy access to 35W. description:
Recently sold: $300,000. **OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 3/23 @ 10-11 AM**

Don't miss your chance to rent a charming 2BR duplex in a fantastic location! This unit is on the main level of an up/down duplex. 2 spacious bedrooms. 1 Bathroom. Large, open living room. Large kitchen with granite countertops. Hardwood floors throughout. Lots of light! Access to a shared basement used for storage. Washer/Dryer is in shared basement, but dedicated to this unit only (washer and dryer not shared). Backyard partially fenced. Access to 1 car stall of a 2 car detached garage. Long driveway for additional off-street parking.

This duplex is located in West Richfield, near the Edina border. Close to bus-lines and Hwy 62 & Hwy 35. Lots of amenities nearby including restaurants such as: PF Changs, Cheesecake factory, Pizza Luce, Fireside Foundry, and Davanni's. Nearby grocery stores include: Aldi's and Lund's/Byerly's. Minutes from Southdale Shopping Center, Galleria, Fairview Southdale Hospital, Centennial Lakes, and Wood Lake Nature Center.

Rental Terms:
* Tenant Responsible for: Gas, Electric, Phone, Cable/Internet, and Yard/Snow Care
* Landlord Responsible for: Trash, Water/Sewer
* 12 Month Lease
* $1475 Security Deposit + First Month's Rent due at lease signing
* Dogs/Cats ok with prior approval, Signed Pet Addendum, Pet Security Deposit, and Additional Pet Rent; size/breed/number restrictions may apply
* Available 4/1 (early move in possible)
* $45/adult application/credit fee
* Non-Smoking
